Package com.fgonzalesv.assignment4

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CourseDBElement
    CourseDBElement implements Comparable, and consists of five attributes: the Course ID (a String), the CRN (an int), the number of credits (an int), the room number (a String), and the instructor name (a String).
    CourseDBManager
    The data manager allows the user to read the courses from a text file or to enter the data in the GUI, and print out the database elements.
    CourseDBStructure
    It is the data structure class that is used with the Course Database Manager class.
